OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FNo 10 held a "dismissive approach" to
OL,8,Fvetting in Peter Mandelson's case,
OL,9,Fwhich created an "atmosphere of
OL,10,Fpressure", sacked Foreign Office
OL,11,Fofficial Sir Olly Robbins has said.
OL,13,FThe former top official is giving
OL,14,Fevidence to MPs over his handling of
OL,15,Fthe vetting process for Mandelson's
OL,16,Fappointment as US ambassador.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FRobbins was sacked by the prime
OL,8,Fminister last week for "deliberately"
OL,9,Fkeeping him in the dark over
OL,10,FMandelson's failure to pass security
OL,11,Fvetting checks before he was appointed.
OL,13,FBut speaking in front of the Foreign
OL,14,FAffairs Committee on Tuesday, Robbins
OL,15,Fsaid there had been pressure from
OL,16,FDowning Street to clear the
OL,17,Fappointment, and an expectation that
OL,18,FMandelson "needed to be in post and in
OL,19,FAmerica as quickly as humanly
OL,20,Fpossible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FRobbins said there had been "very
OL,8,Ffrequent communication" with the
OL,9,Fprivate office at Downing Street
OL,10,Fregarding Mandelson's appointment.
OL,12,F"There was an atmosphere of constant
OL,13,Fchasing," he told MPs, adding there
OL,14,Fwas "never any interest, as far as I
OL,15,Fcan recall, in whether (Mandelson had
OL,16,Fpassed checks), but only an interest
OL,17,Fin when."
OL,26,@tD@AOUwD@XpmxD@Npn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FThe former permanent secretary
OL,8,Fsuggested that the decision to vet
OL,9,FMandelson at all had been under
OL,10,Fdiscussion between the Foreign Office
OL,11,Fand No 10.
OL,13,F"There was a debate between the
OL,14,FCabinet Office and the Foreign Office
OL,15,Fabout how to make sure (Mandelson) is
OL,16,Fsent out to post with the appropriate
OL,17,Fclearance, and that took several days.
OL,26,@wD@XpmwD@bpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,F"A position taken from the Cabinet
OL,8,FOffice was that there was no need to
OL,9,Fvet Mandelson. He was a member of the
OL,10,FHouse of Lords, he was a Privy
OL,11,Fcouncillor.
OL,13,F"In the end, the Foreign Office
OL,14,Finsisted and put its foot down. I
OL,15,Funderstand that my predecessor had to
OL,16,Fbe very firm in person."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FRobbins - who came to the post in
OL,8,FJanuary 2025, once the vetting process
OL,9,Fwas already underway - was keen to
OL,10,Femphasise that Mandelson's vetting was
OL,11,Fcarried out, "rigorously".
OL,13,F"Whilst there was an atmosphere of
OL,14,Fpressure, the department rigorously
OL,15,Ffollowed the process and we did so
OL,16,Ffrankly, as I understand it, despite
OL,17,Fsome in government believing it was
OL,18,Fnot a process we ever needed to
OL,19,Ffollow," he said.
OL,21,F"Sensible precaution" was missed
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FRobbins told MPs that part of the
OL,8,Fissue for No 10 was that Mandelson's
OL,9,Fappointment had been announced before
OL,10,Fsecurity clearance had been decided.
OL,12,F"It's a particularly sensitive issue
OL,13,Fbecause the United States government
OL,14,Fis very hot on clearances people hold,
OL,15,Fand so it would have been a sensible
OL,16,Fprecaution."
OL,18,FDeciding against granting clearance
OL,19,Fwould have caused a "real problem",
OL,20,FRobbins said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,F"I was very conscious that if we went
OL,8,Fthrough the rigour of our process and
OL,9,Fdecided against granting clearance,
OL,10,Fthat would have caused a real problem
OL,11,Ffor our government and a problem for
OL,12,Four country.
OL,14,F"I was conscious of that, without
OL,15,Fletting it influence my judgement, let
OL,16,Falone transferring any of that
OL,17,Fatmosphere on the people charged with
OL,18,Factually making that assessment."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FHe said that removing Mandelson from
OL,8,Fthe process and trying to change the
OL,9,Fperson nominated for the Washington
OL,10,Frole would have caused problems
OL,11,Fbecause the US had already agreed the
OL,12,Fpeer as an acceptable candidate while
OL,13,FJoe Biden was still in office.
OL,15,F"The process of getting agreement was
OL,16,Ftaken at quite some pace and was
OL,17,Fdelivered, I think still technically,
OL,18,Fjust by one working day by the Biden
OL,19,Fadministration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,F"I think if the nomination had changed
OL,8,Fafter that point, the incoming
OL,9,Fadministration may well have commented
OL,10,Fon it publicly, and it would, yes,
OL,11,Fhave caused quite an issue in the
OL,12,Frelationship."
OL,14,FBut Robbins did point out that a due
OL,15,Fdiligence process was carried out
OL,16,Fbefore Mandelson's appointment, and
OL,17,Fprior to the vetting process by the
OL,18,FForeign Office - the results of which
OL,19,FStarmer would have been made aware.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FHe appeared to criticise the prime
OL,8,Fminister's judgement following that
OL,9,Fdue diligence process.
OL,11,F"I regret that the due diligence
OL,12,Fprocess, which threw up, as I
OL,13,Funderstand it, serious reputational
OL,14,Frisks did not colour the prime
OL,15,Fminister's judgement," he said,
OL,16,Fimplying that he believed the PM
OL,17,Fshould have decided against the
OL,18,Fappointment well before the DV process
OL,19,Fbegan.
OL,21,FA "borderline case"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FMandelson was granted developed
OL,8,Fvetting (DV) status despite concerns
OL,9,Fraised by UK Security Vetting (UKSV),
OL,10,Fthe agency that carries out checks.
OL,12,FThe links did not relate to the peer's
OL,13,Flinks to disgraced financier Jeffrey
OL,14,FEpstein, Robbins said.
OL,16,FHe told MPs he was briefed that UKSV
OL,17,Fconsidered Mandelson a "borderline
OL,18,Fcase... leaning towards recommending
OL,19,Fthat clearance is denied".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FThe Foreign Office's security chief
OL,8,Fassessed that the risks could be
OL,9,F"managed and mitigated", a judgement
OL,10,FRobbins told MPs was "not unusual".
OL,12,FHe said that clearance was therefore
OL,13,Fgranted, meaning that when Starmer
OL,14,Ftold MPs the "proper process had been
OL,15,Ffollowed... he was correct".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FThe PM endured two-and-a-half hours of
OL,8,Fbruising questions from MPs on Monday,
OL,9,Fin which he strongly blamed Robbins
OL,10,Ffor "deliberately" and "repeatedly"
OL,11,Fkeeping him in the dark over the
OL,12,Ffailure to receive a green light from
OL,13,FUKSV.
OL,15,FBut Robbins told MPs that ministers
OL,16,Fwere not usually informed of any
OL,17,Ffindings from the vetting process
OL,18,Fapart from the outcome.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FRobbins' comments may go some way to
OL,8,Fvindicating Starmer, as they support
OL,9,Fthe prime minister's claims that he
OL,10,Fwas not aware of the DV process
OL,11,Ffindings.
OL,13,FHe said he had considered asking the
OL,14,Fsee the UKSV documentation after
OL,15,FMandelson was sacked in September last
OL,16,Fyear, but was blocked by doing so.
OL,18,F"My team consulted the Cabinet Office
OL,19,Fand were told that I required a
OL,20,Fnational security justification," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FBadenoch says evidence "devastating"
OL,8,Ffor Starmer
OL,10,FKemi Badenoch responded by saying "the
OL,11,Fevidence from Olly Robbins is
OL,12,Fdevastating to Keir Starmer.
OL,14,F"It is clear the No 10 not only made
OL,15,Fthe appointment before vetting was
OL,16,Fcompleted, but that Mandelson was
OL,17,Falready acting as the ambassador
OL,18,Fbefore the vetting - even seeing
OL,19,Fhighly classified documents," the Tory
OL,20,Fleader said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1776867068
OL,3,COlly Robbins: No 10 created
OL,4,C'atmosphere of pressure' over
OL,5,CMandelson vetting
OL,7,FBadenoch added: "With this, and the
OL,8,F'constant pressure' No 10 applied to
OL,9,Fthe appointment with their 'dismissive
OL,10,Fattitude' to vetting Mandelson, it is
OL,11,Fnow absolutely clear that 'full due
OL,12,Fprocess' was not followed.
OL,14,F"Keir Starmer has misled the House."
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/17
